{"tid":1570485,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"教你喺AWS整返個免費嘅VPN Server","createTime":"2019-09-15T06:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:48:07.000Z","uid":12032,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"05301a375b5ed348971a5585621846d9bf05a1a2","tid":1570485,"uid":12032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:00:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TL;DR</span></span><br />\n1. 註冊AWS account<br />\n2. 去 Cloudformation 轉 Region<br />\n3. Create Stack, 然後用S3 URL<br />\n    <span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://aws-ec2-integrated-vpn-server.s3.ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/template.yaml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faws-ec2-integrated-vpn-server.s3.ap-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftemplate.yaml&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=dfe7f915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aws-ec2-integrated-vpn-server.s3.ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/template.yaml</a></span>， next<br />\n4. 打Stack Name, 同改密碼(可改可唔改)<br />\n5. Next, next and Create<br />\n6. 第佢起好，睇Output<br />\n<br />\nAWS 全名 Amazon Web Service，係全球最大嘅Cloud Provider.<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.amazonwebservices.com/blog/2019/gartner_iaas_mq_2019_800px_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.amazonwebservices.com%2Fblog%2F2019%2Fgartner_iaas_mq_2019_800px_1.jpg&h=36ac1a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁點解會用到AWS呢？因為佢會為各個新用户提供一年嘅免費方案，即係有一部份嘅服務可以比用戶免費試用<br />\n技術嘢我就唔講咁多<br />\n而個VPN Server係可以免費開足一年，同埋每個月有15GB免費用，用過後會收費, USD $0.02 / GB<br />\n<br />\n整好之後，你會有L2TP, PPTP 同Shadowsocks, 咩嚟我唔講，自己Google, 返正 iPhone Windows 都用到。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一</span>，開返個AWS account 先啦。<br />\n比錢就會用到信用卡，建議用Tap &amp; Go (用緊) / Mastercard Prepaid Gift Card (未試過)<br />\n點開就唔多講<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fredhsieh.com/how-to-start-aws/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fredhsieh.com%2Fhow-to-start-aws%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=14e49b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fredhsieh.com/how-to-start-aws/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://oranwind.org/-aws-zhu-ce-aws-zhang-hao/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foranwind.org%2F-aws-zhu-ce-aws-zhang-hao%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=4d007834\" target=\"_blank\">https://oranwind.org/-aws-zhu-ce-aws-zhang-hao/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://jerrynest.io/signup-aws/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjerrynest.io%2Fsignup-aws%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=ac6834db\" target=\"_blank\">https://jerrynest.io/signup-aws/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二</span>，註冊完就去Cloudformation.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得轉Region(右上角), 強力建議去Singapore, 因為Hong Kong開機冇得免費!!!</span></span><br />\n然後㩒 Create Stack<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHEZtZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHEZtZn.png&h=2bc2902b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三</span>，喺Specify an Amazon S3 template URL 輸入<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://aws-ec2-integrated-vpn-server.s3.ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/template.yaml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faws-ec2-integrated-vpn-server.s3.ap-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftemplate.yaml&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=dfe7f915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://aws-ec2-integrated-vpn-server.s3.ap-east-1.amazonaws.com/template.yaml</a></span></span> 然後繼續<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qM6EtZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqM6EtZM.png&h=53af005f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第四</span>，輸入Stack Name, 同埋改左個Password(optional)，然後繼續<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5uzbj8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5uzbj8D.png&h=98b32580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第五，第六</span>，都係繼續，最後Create<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHKVMPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHKVMPb.png&h=4cb93d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2Ojt2x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2Ojt2x.png&h=1b2e183d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後</span></span>，等佢起完(一分鐘左右)，去Output 睇返VPN 啲Credential,搞掂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOmEt20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOmEt20.png&h=4ce5beea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用完唔要就直接Delete左個Stack佢。<br />\n<br />\n測速<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDaRkgv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDaRkgv.png&h=57673bc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efbf36eaf7c1594991548d1cf8fe447dc9a32716","tid":1570485,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e1a00deb36cdbdb36f4127e8491e85af263d73","tid":1570485,"uid":12032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"6a8ca78b0d8da09c470162117b78507690feff01","tid":1570485,"uid":81071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"點解揀新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc65b24d0bff1c5b8d0363d5c4638669f5a4577","tid":1570485,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8a4b0319b423327716bd8e1d5c3439e721b85d","tid":1570485,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:05: